    "class": "subclass:bladesinging",
    "level": 2,
    "name": "Training in War and Song",
    "description": "When you adopt this tradition, you gain proficiency with light armor, and you gain proficiency with one type of one-handed melee weapon of your choice. You also gain proficiency in the Performance skill if you don't already have it.",
